c=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e199ef0b071a1fbe2e7d16825775f07819367c7","tid":2356787,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e3f5adec476ec6baad1f285a04689bb25318b9","tid":2356787,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"官：案情嚴重   判刑須具阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n裁判官鍾明新判刑時指，雖然接納被告背景及成績良好，但案例指出，社會服務令並不適用於嚴重案件，而案情及案發時的社會政治氣氛均屬考慮因素。而本案案情屬於嚴重，被告當時帶備口罩、面罩、護目鏡等示威者裝束。涉案的伸縮棍長 24 - 55 厘米，是有效武器、殺傷力不少，可重複使用，亦是放置於可以隨時取出的位置。由於案情屬於嚴重，社會服務令並不合適。而勞教中心報告則指，被告因體能問題，不適合接受勞教。考慮被告年輕初犯、背景良好及有悔意，決定按報告建議，判處更生中心。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E7%AF%80-%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-sing-%E8%AA%8D%E6%94%9C%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E6%A3%8D-%E6%87%89%E5%B1%86-dse-%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E5%88%A4%E6%9B%B4%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-sing-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%2594%259C%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B1%2586-dse-%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5qjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=39423fa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-sing-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%2594%259C%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B1%2586-dse-%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&h=0b5896ed\" data-auto-link targ